	<term>color reference</term>
	<definition><p>Any valid way of describing a particular color that LiveCode can understand.</p>
<p></p>
<p>Colors can be referred to by color name, <glossary tag="HTML">HTML</glossary>-style specification, or as three comma-separated numbers between zero and 255 (one for each of red, blue, and green).</p></definition>
